{
  "message": "feat(dashboard): add split view layout with VM preview\n\nAdd a split view to the fleet page where clicking a VM row opens a preview\npanel on the right side. The preview shows task details, status, metrics\nplaceholders, and action buttons.\n\n- Updated fleet.html with flex layout (3/5 + 2/5 split when preview active)\n- Added /preview/vm/{id} endpoint returning partial HTML for htmx\n- Created vm_preview.html template with status badge, metrics grid, and actions\n- Selected VM row gets blue highlight styling\n- Preview panel slides in with Alpine.js transitions\n- Hidden on small screens (lg:block)\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
